Text: Rebecca and Tommy are coming to townPST Howdy everyone Rebecca myself and the pumpkin will be gracing the Great State of Texas in late Feb During this time we will be hosting a post wedding reception on Sunday the th of February at the Coliseum Restaurant in Clear Lake We plan on starting the party at around It will be a semi formal type of occasion so just bring an appetite and get ready for a great afternoon If you could please let us know via email if you can make it and if you will be bringing a significant other we would greatly appreciate it We look forward to seeing everyone there Tommy GO STELLERS Send and receive Hotmail on your mobile device

Hello Phillywhats up man How are things with you Hearing all the news about Enron and all figured I see how you are fairing I really hope that your not effected by all the bs We are doing well here Getting cold but hey its Norway right We have starting building a house and its going well I figure it will take about a year to get it all done I would like to do as much of the work myself but I will see how long that goes Anyway The Family and myself will be in Houston in late Feb We are having a small reception in Clear Lake and would love to see yall there if you can make it Let me here from you soon hope all is well with you and the family Tell your moms whats up from me Tommy Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at intlasp
